1. Jaeger 설정
    wget https://download.jaegertracing.io/v2.16.0/jaeger-2.16.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz
    tar zxvf jaeger-2.16.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz
    cd jaeger-2.16.0-linux-amd64
    ./jaeger --set=receivers.otlp.protocols.http.endpoint=0.0.0.0:4318

2. 그라파나 및 프로메테우스
    1. 프로메테우스
      1) 설치
    	apt update
    	apt -y install prometheus

      2) 설정
        vi /etc/default/prometheus
            ARGS=""  이걸 변경  ARGS="--enable-feature=exemplar-storage"

        vi /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml 설정 밑에 다음 내용 추가
          - job_name: spring
            metrics_path: '/actuator/prometheus'
            static_configs:
              - targets: ['스프링의 IP주소:8080']

      3) 실행
    	systemctl restart prometheus

    2. 그라파나
      1) 설치
    	wget -q -O /usr/share/keyrings/grafana.key https://packages.grafana.com/gpg.key
    	echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/grafana.key] https://packages.grafana.com/oss/deb stable main" | tee -a /etc/apt/sources.list.d/grafana.list

    	apt update
    	apt -y install grafana


      2) 실행
    	systemctl restart grafana-server

